| extend MetricKind = 'Failures'

    | where name == "HeartbeatState" and cloud_RoleName != ''
    | distinct cloud_RoleName, cloud_RoleInstance;

    | where name == "HeartbeatState"
    | summarize ServiceTime = max(timestamp) by cloud_RoleName, cloud_RoleInstance
    | where ServiceTime > ago(6m);

services
| project cloud_RoleName, cloud_RoleInstance, Status = "Not Available"
| join kind=leftanti available on cloud_RoleName and cloud_RoleInstance
